'''Igbo-Ukwu''' bu obodo di na Okpuru ochichi Aguata, na onuochichi [[Anambra State|Anambra]], na owuwa anyanwu nke [[Naigeria]]. Ihe amarakali Igbo-Ukwu bu maka olu-aka ha. Igbo-ukwu bu obodo eji oru aka di ka ikpu uzu na umu ihe ndi ozo were mara .
