'''Incumbent''' bu mkpuru okwu ndi bekee adi ji kpo onye no na office, di lu ogu ta o no na office nka. Nke bu na oge ''election''.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[President of Naigeria]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

'''Asụsụ obodo''' bu mkpuru okwu ndi [[bekee]] ana-kpo olu ndi madu n'otu ala di ji kwu eku.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[English language]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Usòrò:Icon 01016 Zhertvoprinoshenie Avraama.jpg|thumbnail]] '''Abraham''' bu aha [[nwoke]]. Obu kwaa aha onye bidoro umu Israel. Ihe o kuru mgbe odi ndu bu he bidoro ekpere chi ana-kpo ''[[Judaism]]''.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Jisọs Kraịst]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Usòrò:LocationArctic.png|thumb|right|250px|Ala Arctic n'uwa.]] Ala '''Arktik''' bu ala di ju oyi no n'elu uwa. Ala ahu nile bu miri shiri ike.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Antarctica]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

Onye '''Chrisitan''' bu onye bi na echiche adi-kpo ''[[Christianity]]''.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Efefe Kraịst]] * [[Muslim]] * [[Jews]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Ákwúkwó orünotu:Menorah7a.png|thumb|Menorah]] '''Judaism''' bu ekpere chi nde umu Israel, nde ''Hebrew'' na ''Jews''. Onye ana-kpo [[Jesus Christ]] bula onye Jew.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Christianity]] * [[Islam]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

Onye '''Jew''' bu onye bi na ekpere chi ana-kpo ''[[Judaism]]''. Ndi na bu ndi agadi umu [[Abraham]], bu nde mbu.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Judaism]] * [[Christian]] * [[Muslim]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Usòrò:Prayer in Cairo 1865.jpg|thumb|250px]] '''Ndi áláküba''' bu onye bi na ekpere chi ana-kpo ''[[Islam]]''.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Islam]] * [[Christian]] * [[Jews]]
---- {{Commons category|Muslims}}
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Usòrò:Israel in its region (pre 1967 territory).svg|thumb|250px|Israel]] [[Usòrò:Flag of Israel.svg|thumbnail|áká_ịkẹngạ]] '''Israel''' bu otu obodo no n'ala ukwu ana-kpo [[Asia]]. Mgbe mbu, o bula obodo nde umu [[Abraham]]. Na mgbe gara-aga, mgbe adila kpo Israel "Judea", isi oche ya bula [[ama ukwu]] okeye ana-kpo ''Jerusalem''.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Abraham]] * [[Jews]] * [[Jesus Christ]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Ákwúkwó orünotu:Football4.png|right|thumb|250px|Football]] '''Football''' bu eguregu eji aku na uku. N'ebe [[USA|America]] na [[Canada]], ma mgbe ufodu na ala bekee, adiwi kpo ya ''soccer''.
==Links na aga n'ezi== * ''[http://www.fifa.com/ Federation Internationale de Football Association (FIFA)]'' * [http://www.cafonline.com/ Confederation of African Football (CAF)]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

{{Ngwómárí Obodo |native_name = Australia |conventional_long_name = Égómadunílé nke Ostraliya |common_name = Ostraliya |image_flag = Flag of Australia.svg |image_coat = Coat of Arms of Australia.svg | symbol_type = Ihü | image_map = Australia (orthographic projection).svg | map_width = 220px |asusu_obodo = [[Bekee]] }}
'''Ostraliya''' (''Australia'') bu ala ukwu no n'akpuru uwa. Dika [[Afrịka]], obu ala aja. Ostraliya bu ala gụnyere [[Chile]] nke Australian Afrịka, n'àgwàetiti [[Tasmania]], na ọtụtụ ekpri isuo. Ọ bụ n'ụwa nke isii-kasị ala site mkpokọta n'ógbè ahụ.
Ostraliya a mmadụ bi n'ihi na 40.000 isua. Amaala Ostraliya okwu n'asụsụ grouped n'ime Olee ihe enyemaka 250 asụsụ dị iche iche.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Békè']]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Continents]] [[Òtù:Obodo]]

[[Ákwúkwó orünotu:Arctic Ocean.png|right|200px|Arctic Ocean]] Oke osimiri nke ana kpo '''''Artic Ocean''''' bu oke osimiri ntakiri e kere mgbe a kewasiri-ekewa [[Osimiri uwa]] n'ise. O bu osimiri nke e kere ano. O no n'elu ala uwa nile, ebe [[Arctic]].
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Southern Ocean|Antarctic Ocean]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Usòrò:Wikipedia-logo-v2-en.png|right]] '''English Wikipedia''' bu aha ana-kpo otu ''[[Wikipedia]]'' bu na olu [[bekee]]. Wikipedia ahu vuru ivu, bu nke Wikipedia mbu e mere 15 Jenụwarị na afo 2001.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Wikimedia]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọr ''Gregorian'', '''Ọktoba''' bu onwa iri na afo, bu otu onwa n'ime asaa nwere ubochi ruru 31 (''iri ato na otu'') n'ime wo. Na mgbe gara-aga, Ọktoba bula onwa asato, site na afo nwela onwa iri. Afo nwere onwa iri na abwo ubochi kena.

{{Commons|Ọktoba}}

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Ọktoba]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}
Na ogúafọr nde ''Julian'' ma ''Gregorian'', '''Jenụwarị''' bu onwa mbu na afo nile, bu otu onwa n'ime asaa nwere ubochi ruru 31 (''iri ato na otu''). Ma ubochi kena, otu afo nwere onwa iri na abuo.

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Önwa mbu]]
[[Òtù:Önwa (ogẹ)]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafor nke ''Julian'' ma ''Gregorian'', '''Febrụwarị''' bu onwa abuo na afo nile, bu onwa n'eweghi ubochi ruru 30 (''iri ato''). Mgbe afo bu na oge ana-kpo ''leap year'', Febrụwarị nwere ubochi ruru 29 (''iri abuo na iteghete''). Oge nile, onwere ubochi ruru 28 (''iri abuo na asato'').

[[Òtù:Febrụwarị]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọ''Gregorian'', '''Eprel''' bu onwa ano na afo, nwere ubochi ruru 30 (iri ato). Na mgbe gara-aga, Eprel bula onwa abua, site na afo nwela onwa iri. Mgbe ekere ''[[Jenụwarị]]'' na ''[[Febrụwarị]]'', Eprel a-da, mee afo nwere onwa iri na abuo.

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Önwa ànó]]
[[Òtù:Önwa (ogẹ)]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọ ''Gregorian'', '''Mee''' bu onwa ise na afo, bu otu onwa n'ime asaa nwere ubochi ruru 31 (iri ato na otu).

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Mee]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na ogúafọr Gregorian, '''Juun''' bu onwa isii na afo. O nwere ubochi ruru 30 (iri ato).

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Önwa ishií]]
[[Òtù:Önwa (ogẹ)]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Ime oguafọr ''Gregorian'', '''Julaị''' bu onwa asato na afo, bu otu onwa n'ime asaa nwere ubochi ruru 31 (''iri ato na otu''). Na mgbe gara-aga, Julaị bula onwa ise mgbe adila kpo ya ''Quintilis''. Otu afo nwela onwa iri. Mgbe ekere ''[[Jenụwarị]]'' na ''[[Febrụwarị]]'', Julaị a-da, mee otu afo nwere onwa iri na abuo.

[[Òtù:Julaị]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọr ''Gregorian'', '''Ọgọọst ''' bu onwa asato na afo, bu otu onwa n'ime asaa nwere ubochi ruru 31 (''iri ato na otu'') n'ime wo. Na mgbe gara-aga, Ọgọọst  bula onwa isii ma mgbe adila kpo ya ''Sextilis''. Otu afo nwela onwa iri mgbe ahu. Ubochi kena, afo nwere onwa iri na abuo.

[[Òtù:Ọgọọst]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọr ''Gregorian'', '''Septemba''' bu onwa iteghete na afo, nwere ubochi ruru 30 (''iri ato''). Na mgbe gara-aga, Septemba bula onwa asaa, site na afo a-di enwela ''[[Jenụwarị]]'' na ''[[Febrụwarị]]''. Mgbe ekere wo, otu afo enweta onwa iri na abuo.

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Septemba]]

{{Íshí nke önwa}}

Na iguafọr ''Gregorian'', '''Novemba''' bu onwa iri na otu, na afo. O nwere ubochi ruru 30 (''iri ato''). Mgbe gara-aga, Novemba bula onwa iteghete, site na afo nwela onwa iri. Afo nwere onwa iri na abwo ubochi kena.

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Novemba]]

'''Mmuo Nso''' bu mmuo nke oma ndi ekpere chi [[Jisos Kraist]]. Obu mmuo bu enyi [[Chineke]] wo kere uwa.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Chineke]] * [[Ekwensu]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

:''Lee [[1 (disambiguation)|'''"1"''' nke-na]].'' '''Otu (1)''' bu [[onu agugu]] mbu. Onu agugu nke [[abụo]] soto ya.
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[2 (disambiguation)|'''"2"''' nke-na]].'' '''Abụo (2)''' bu [[onu agugu]] no n'etiti nke [[otu|mbu]] na onu agugu nke [[atọ]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[3 (disambiguation)|'''"3"''' nke-na]].'' '''Atọ (3)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti [[abụo]] na [[anọ]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[4 (disambiguation)|'''"4"''' nke-na]].'' '''Anọ (4)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti [[atọ]] n'[[ise]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[5 (disambiguation)|'''"5"''' nke-na]].'' '''Ise (5)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti [[anọ]] na [[isii]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[6 (disambiguation)|'''"6"''' nke-na]].'' '''Isii (6)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti [[ise]] na [[asaa]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[7 (disambiguation)|'''7''' nke-na]].'' '''Asaa (7)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no na etiti onu ogugu nke [[isii]] na [[asatọ]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[8 (disambiguation)|'''"8"''' nke-na]].'' '''Asatọ (8)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti onu agugu nke [[asaa]] na [[iteghete]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[9 (disambiguation)|'''9''' nke-na]].'' Nke bu otu [[onu agugu]] nk'ana-kpo '''iteghete''', kpo-kwa '''itolu'''. O no n'etiti [[asatọ]] na [[iri]].
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

:''Lee [[10 (disambiguation)|'''"10"''' nke-na]].'' '''Iri (10)''' bu otu [[onu agugu]]. O no n'etiti [[iteghete]] na [[iri na otu]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}
[[Òtù:Onu agugu]]

'''Amaigbo''' bu obodo okenye [[ndị Igbo]] no n'[[Imo State]] la Naigeria. Obodo na a-nola nga, n'ebe ana-kpo Igboland na oge ruru ogologo. Amuru nwoke ana-kpo Jaja, nwoke bidoro Opobo, na Amaigbo.

{{ÉdéNtạ}}

[[Òtù:Ama ukwu nor na Naigeria]]

[[Usòrò:WM2006 0060.jpg|thumb|200px|right|[[Jimbo Wales]], onye bidoro [[Wikipedia]].]] Nde bu '''ndi ocha''' bu ndi mmadu, nke ana hu na obodo ukwu bu [[Europe]] ma ebe ozo na nnukwu, nwere ahu di cha ocha.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Ndi oji]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

Onye bu '''Moderate''' bu onye no n'etiti echiche abuo, na choro iso wo eso maka otu ha diwo emee he. Na ekpere chi na politics, ndi moderate bu ndi bu n'etiti ndi [[Liberal]] ma ndi [[Conservative]]. Ha nwere ike so onye ha choro.
==Lee nke ozo== * [[Conservative]] * [[Liberal]]
{{ÉdéNtạ}}

