'''Ibrahim Shekarau''' (amuru [[Ise|5]] [[Novemba]] 1955) bu onye governor ndi bi na [[Kano State]] na [[Naigeria]]. Amuru ya na [[Kano]], obodo city bu isi state ahu. Obukwa onye [[All Nigeria People's Party]].
