==Bureaucrats==

{{IguafọrÖnwa-ụzụ-Alụsị|float=right}}
1 Jenụwarị bu ubochi mbu na onwa ana-kpo [[Jenụwarị]]. Obukwa nke mbu na afo nile. Anyi nwere agugu ubochi 364 (365 na afo ana-kpo ''leap year'') tupu afo na agwu.
==Ihe mere na Önwa mbu 1== * 1901 - Ndi [[bekee]] emee [[Naigeria]] ''protectorate''. * 1960 - Ndi [[Cameroon]] nweta ala wo mgbe ndi [[France]] ma ndi [[bekee]] hafuru. * [[2000]] - Emee [[Hama Amadou]] onye [[prime minister]] obodo [[Niger]]. ==Onye amuru==
==Onye wuru==
