{{Infobox Dotcom company | company_name = XVideos | company_logo = [[File:Xvideos.gif|200px]] | company_type = [[Akpali agụụ mmekọahụ]] | genre = Porn | foundation = | founder = | location = [[Njikota Obodo Amerika]] | area_served = Worldwide | industry = Porn | products = | services = Akpali agụụ mmekọahụ | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | owner = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | company_slogan = Free Porn Videos | url = xvideos.com | screenshot = | caption = | alexa = {{DecreasePositive}} 41 ({{as of|2014|6|25|alt=June 2014}})<ref name="alexa">{{cite web|url= http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/xvideos.com |title= Xvideos.com Site Info | publisher= [[Alexa Internet]] |accessdate= 2014-04-01 }}</ref><!--Updated monthly by OKBot.--> | website_type = Akpali agụụ mmekọahụ video nkekọrịta | language = [[Asụsụ Inglish|Inglish]] | advertising = Ee | registration = ịnara | launch_date = [[1997]] | current_status = Ifịk ifịk | footnotes = | intl = }}
'''XVideos''' bụ free akpali agụụ mmekọahụ video òkè website. Ọ bụ ihe ndị kasị ewu ewu na akpali agụụ mmekọahụ website ke ererimbot, ọ imeri Pornhub ka kasị ewu ewu na okenye video òkè website ke Novemba [[2010]]. Ọ na-onwe LiveJasmin, otu okenye video chat website ke Jenuari [[2012]].
Dị ka [[Alexa Internet|Alexa]] ọ dịla otu 50 kasị ewu ewu na weebụsaịtị na Ịntanetị ebe ọ bụ na n'oge [[2013]], ma ugbua ihe 350 nde kwa ọnwa ọbịa, na-enye "na 29 petabytes data okpụhọ kwa ọnwa."<ref name="ExtremeTech">{{cite journal |url= http://www.extremetech.com/computing/123929-just-how-big-are-porn-sites |title=Just how big are porn sites? |first=Sebastian |last=Anthony |journal=[[ExtremeTech]] |location=New York, NY |publisher=[[Ziff Davis Media]] |date=April 4, 2012 |accessdate=April 7, 2012 |oclc=489265532}}</ref>
