'''Bochotnica''' ([[:en:International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] : [bɔxɔtˈnit͡sa]) bụ [[ogbè]] no na South-Eastern ala ana-kpo [[Poland]]. Ono n'etiti obodo [[Puławy]] na [[Lublin]], obodo no n'ime Poland, ebe miri ogologo (''river'') ana-kpo [[Wisła]].

==Links na aga n'ezi==
* [http://www.kazimierzdolny.pl/bochotnica/28081/ Bochotnica].

