{{infobox disease
| name           = Nje ọrịa Ebola
| image          = 7042 lores-Ebola-Zaire-CDC Photo.jpg
| caption        = Foto ndị nlekọta onyeọrịa ndị guzo n’ihu [[MayingaN'Seka|Mayinga N.]]1976,bụ onye nje ọrịa Ebola ji; ọnwụrụ mgbe ụbọchị ole na ole gasịrị na nje ọrịa Ebola. Ọnwụrụ ka ụbochị ole na ole gasịrị mgbe ọbara gbasịrị ya n’ime ahụ.
| DiseasesDB     = 18043
| ICD10          = {{ICD10|A|98|4|a|90}}
| ICD9           = {{ICD9|065.8}}
| MedlinePlus    = 001339
| eMedicineSubj  = med
| eMedicineTopic = 626
| MeshID         = D019142
}}
'''Nje ọrịa Ebola''' ('''EVD''') maọbụ '''Ajọ ọrịa ọbara nke Ebola''' ('''EHF''') bụ ọrịa nke n'emetụta ndị mmadụ nke [[nje ebola]] n'akpata.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Ọ na ewelite isi abalị abụọ ruo izu ụka atọ mgbe onye ahụ nwetara nje ahụ, tinyere [[oyi]], ọnya akpịrị, [[mgburisi ahụ|ahụ mgbu]], na [[isiọwụwa]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> N'ụzọ doro anya [[afọ ntụgharị]], agbọ, na [[afọ ọsịsa]] n'esonye, tinyere mbelata ịrụ ọrụ nke [[umeji]] and [[akụrụ]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> N'ogo a, ụfọdụ n'ebido [[gbawa ọbara]].<ref name=WHO2014>{{cite web|title=Ebola virus disease  Fact sheet N°103|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs103/en/|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=12 April 2014|date=March 2014}}</ref>

<!-- Ihe n'akpata ya na nnyocha-->
Enwere ike ibute nje a site n'inwe mmekọrịta site na [[ọbara]] maọbụ [[mmiri si n'ime ahụ pụta]] nke anụmanụ ọdị n'ahụ (dịka enwe  maọbụ[[ụsụ n'ata mkpụrụ osisi]]).<ref name=WHO2014/> Enwebeghị ndekọ enwere maka nkesa ya site n'ikuku nke ebe obibi.<ref name=WHOAir2014>{{cite web|title=2014 Ebola Virus Disease (EVD) outbreak in West Africa|url=http://www.who.int/ith/updates/20140421/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=3 August 2014|date=Apr 21 2014}}</ref> Achọpụtara na ụsụ n'ata mkpụrụ osisi ga-enwe ike buru ma kesaa ya n'ebuteghị nje ahụ.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Ozugbo mmadụ butere ya, nje a n'efe ndịọzọ.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Ụmụnwoke ndị lanahụrụ ya ga-ebunye nje a site na  [[mkpụrụ ndụ nwoke]] ihe ruru ọnwa abụọ.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Iji mee nnyocha ọrịa ndịọzọ ndị eji nke yiri nke a mara dịka, [[ịba]], [[afọ ọsịsa]] na ndịọzọ [[Ajọ ọrịa n'efe efe]]ka ebu ụzọ wepu.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Iji hụụ n'enyochara ọbara maka kịrịkịrị nje [[ihe ndị n'alụso nje ọgụ n'ime ahụ]], kịrịkịrị nje [[RNA]],maọbụ nje n'onwe ya.<ref name=WHO2014/>

<!-- Mgbochi -->
Mgbochi gụnyere ibelata nkesa ọrịa a site na enwe na ezi ruo na mmadụ.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Apụrụ ime nke a site n'ilebara anụmanụ ndị ọrịa a ji, igbu ha n'ibupụ ozu ha ebe kwesịrị maọbụrụ n'achọpụtara ya.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Isi anụ n'ọkụ nke ọma n'iyichi ahụ nke ọma ga-enye aka.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Dịka iyichi ahụ na [[ịkwọ aka]] mgbe ịnọ onye bu ọrịa a nso.<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Ekwesịrị iji nlezianya mee ihe mgbe a na-emetụ mmiri ndị si n'ahụ onye bu ọrịa a na ihe ndị si ya n'ahụ aka.<ref name=WHO2014/>

<!-- Treatment, Prognosis and Epidemiology-->
Onwebeghị ọgwụgwọ ọbụla maka ọrịa a; mgbalị a na-etinye inyere ndị buterela ya aka gụnyere inye dịka [[inye mmiri etinyere nnu]] (ịńụ mmiri dịtụ ụtọ na mmiri nnu dị) maọbụ [[mmiri buru ibu]].<ref name=WHO2014/> Ọrịa a n'egbu [[n'ụdị dị elu]]: n'egbu pasent 50 na 90 bụ ndị butere ya.<ref name=WHO2014/><ref name="Elsevier/Academic Press">{{cite book|author1=C.M. Fauquet|title=Virus taxonomy classification and nomenclature of viruses; 8th report of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses|date=2005|publisher=Elsevier/Academic Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780080575483|page=648|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=9Wy7Jgy5RWYC&pg=PA648}}</ref> Ebu ụzọ chọpụta EVD na [[Sụdan]] na [[mba Kongo]].<!-- <ref name=WHO2014/> --> Ọrịa a n'agbasakarị n'ebe ndị bi n'akụkụ mmiri.<ref name=WHO2014/> Site na 1976 (mgbe eburu ụzọ chọpụta ya) ruo 2013, ihe fọdụrụ nke nta ka oruo 1,000 mmadụ ebutela ya.<ref name=WHO2014/><ref name=MMWRJune2014>{{cite web|title=Ebola Viral Disease Outbreak — West Africa, 2014|url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm6325a4.htm?s_cid=mm6325a4_w|website=CDC|accessdate=26 June 2014|date=June 27, 2014}}</ref> Mgbasa ya dị elu ugbu a. [[2014 Mgbasa Ebola na ọdịda anyanwụ Afrịka]], nke n'emetụta [[Guini]], [[Sierra Leon]], [[Laịberia]] na nke na-emetụ [[Naịjiria]].<ref name=CDC2014>{{cite web|title=CDC urges all US residents to avoid nonessential travel to Liberia, Guinea, and Sierra Leone because of an unprecedented outbreak of Ebola.|url=http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices/warning/ebola-liberia|website=CDC|accessdate=2 August 2014|date=July 31, 2014}}</ref><ref name=CDCAug2014N>{{cite web|title=Outbreak of Ebola in Guinea, Liberia, and Sierra Leone|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/outbreaks/guinea/index.html|website=CDC|accessdate=5 August 2014|date=August 4, 2014}}</ref> N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 2014 achọpụtala mmadụ 1600 ndị bu ọrịa a.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ebola virus disease update - West Africa|url=http://www.who.int/csr/don/2014_08_04_ebola/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=6 August 2014|date=Aug 4, 2014}}</ref> Ana etinye mgbalị ịrụpụta [[ọgwụ mgbochi]]; mana ka ọdị onwebeghị nke dị.<ref name=WHO2014/>

